// Some notes about the ICAD_MN_XXX bitset visibility values:
// Associate the spacers with the items *following* them, if you aren't showing the items,
// don't show the spacer right before them. Keep the ending curly braces way off to the right,
// so it's easier to count parenthesis for grouping.  Leave spaces around things so they are easier to read.
// To combine things, use a vertical bar (pipe?) like ICAD_MN_INT | ICAD_MN_EXP.  To eliminate things,
